Metadata: Marine Advisory Extension Service, Humboldt State University, Arcata, CA

A quarterly publication of the marine advisory extension service, a Sea Grant project, sponsored by the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), U.S. Department of Commerce. Compensation for Lost Fishing Gear - Final Regulations; Galley stoves and heaters; Marine fouling; Farewell to Fred Jurick; Caution: Your television receiver may be hazardous to your Loran-C receivers health; Accuracy of nautical charts; Salmon poisoning; Ocean temperature information; Marine ecosystems explained; What salmon fishing?
